item.title: CVE-2020-6200|2024-08-04T08:55:21.904Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20commerce%20cloud%20%28smartedit%20extension%29
item.description: The SAP Commerce (SmartEdit Extension), versions- 6.6, 6.7, 1808, 1811, is vulnerable to client-side angularjs template injection, a variant of Cross-Site-Scripting (XSS) that exploits the templating facilities of the angular framework.
